        "heading": "Background & Context",
        "content": "The Message Batches API exists because most AI workloads don't need real-time responses. Email processing, dataset labeling, content generation, eval suites ŌĆö these can all wait minutes or hours. Anthropic can schedule batch work during low-demand periods, so they pass the savings on: **50% off both input and output tokens**.\n\nThis isn't a minor optimization. For any pipeline that processes data in bulk, batching is the single easiest cost reduction ŌĆö no code changes to your prompts, no quality trade-offs. Just submit async instead of sync."
