        "content": "### Standard vs. Batch Pricing\n| Model | Standard In/Out | Batch In/Out | Savings |\n|-------|----------------|--------------|---------|\n| Opus 4.6 | $5 / $25 | $2.50 / $12.50 | 50% |\n| Sonnet 4.6 | $3 / $15 | $1.50 / $7.50 | 50% |\n| Haiku 4.5 | $1 / $5 | $0.50 / $2.50 | 50% |\n\n### Real Cost Scenario\n```\nPipeline: 5,000 emails/day, classified + summarized\n  Classify (Haiku):   5K ├Ś 800 in + 50 out = 4M in + 0.25M out\n  Summarize (Sonnet): 5K ├Ś 2K in + 500 out = 10M in + 2.5M out\n\nStandard API:\n  Haiku:  4M ├Ś $1 + 0.25M ├Ś $5   = $4 + $1.25    = $5.25\n  Sonnet: 10M ├Ś $3 + 2.5M ├Ś $15  = $30 + $37.50   = $67.50\n  Daily total: $72.75 ŌåÆ $2,182/month\n\nBatch API:\n  Haiku:  4M ├Ś $0.50 + 0.25M ├Ś $2.50 = $2 + $0.63    = $2.63\n  Sonnet: 10M ├Ś $1.50 + 2.5M ├Ś $7.50 = $15 + $18.75   = $33.75\n  Daily total: $36.38 ŌåÆ $1,091/month\n\n  Savings: $1,091/month (50%)\n```"
