        "content": "### Quick Decision Tree\n```\nSTART HERE\n  Ōöé\n  Ōö£ŌöĆ Is the output format predictable? (labels, categories, extracted fields)\n  Ōöé   YES ŌåÆ HAIKU\n  Ōöé\n  Ōö£ŌöĆ Does it need to generate creative/technical content?\n  Ōöé   YES ŌåÆ Does the content need to be genuinely novel or insightful?\n  Ōöé          NO  ŌåÆ SONNET (most generation tasks)\n  Ōöé          YES ŌåÆ OPUS (only for truly complex generation)\n  Ōöé\n  Ōö£ŌöĆ Does it need to reason across multiple constraints?\n  Ōöé   NO  ŌåÆ SONNET\n  Ōöé   YES ŌåÆ How many constraints and how ambiguous?\n  Ōöé          2-3 clear constraints ŌåÆ SONNET\n  Ōöé          4+ or ambiguous/conflicting ŌåÆ OPUS\n  Ōöé\n  ŌööŌöĆ When in doubt ŌåÆ SONNET (then downgrade/upgrade based on eval data)\n```\n\n### Detailed Task Mapping\n| Task Category | Examples | Model | Why |\n|--------------|---------|-------|-----|\n| **Classification** | Sentiment, spam detection, topic labeling, intent routing | Haiku | Deterministic output, no reasoning chain needed |\n| **Extraction** | Pull names/dates/amounts from text, parse structured data | Haiku | Pattern matching, not synthesis |\n| **Formatting** | Reformat JSON, convert units, template filling | Haiku | Mechanical transformation |\n| **Routing** | Decide which handler/agent to invoke | Haiku | Simple decision tree |\n| **Summarization** | Condense documents, generate TL;DR | Sonnet | Requires understanding, but output is constrained |\n| **Code generation** | Write functions from specs, generate tests | Sonnet | Needs quality, but specs constrain the problem |\n| **Analysis** | Data analysis, trend identification, comparisons | Sonnet | Requires reasoning but within bounded domains |\n| **Content creation** | Blog posts, descriptions, documentation | Sonnet | Quality matters, but patterns are established |\n| **Code review** | Find bugs, suggest improvements, security review | Sonnet | Catches 90%+ of issues at 60% less than Opus |\n| **Architecture** | System design, trade-off analysis, migration planning | Opus | Must hold many constraints simultaneously |\n| **Complex debugging** | Multi-system issues, race conditions, subtle logic errors | Opus | Requires deep reasoning chains |\n| **Prompt engineering** | Designing prompts, meta-reasoning about AI behavior | Opus | Meta-cognitive task, benefits from strongest reasoning |"
